{"tid":512422,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局擬明年初推零售財富管理專業資歷架構 (18:11)","createTime":"2017-12-28T12:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T12:48:06.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ec03fb1c0fb98d9302ba4d1ceda6bf16b7175b54","tid":512422,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20171228/img/20171228181159fi_p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20171228%2Fimg%2F20171228181159fi_p1.jpg&h=8962d392&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=0nV6d5TKzK7hGRrvUqXeLYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=5d9142a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】香港金融管理局宣布，將於明年1月2日推出零售財富管理的銀行專業資歷架構(Enhanced Competency Framework，簡稱ECF)。此前，金管局已就打擊洗錢及恐怖分子資金籌集、網絡安全及財資管理等範疇，推出ECF。<br />\n<br />\n所謂ECF，是指金管局與銀行業界，以及香港銀行學會合作，推行普及的銀行專業資歷架構，成為業界共同採用的能力標準，以更有效培訓新入職者，並促進現有從業員的專業發展。<br />\n<br />\n針對零售財富管理的ECF推出後，金管局指認可機構應積極採用此架構作基準，以提升銀行從業員的核心能力水平及加強持續專業發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20171228/20171228181159fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20171228%2F20171228181159fi.html&d=0nV6d5TKzK7hGRrvUqXeLYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=a6f6b2e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20171228/20171228181159fi.html</a>"}]}